# Secrets — NEVER commit env files (Equoria-07so3). Use *.example templates instead.
# Covers every variant present in the repo: .env, .env.test, env.test, env.beta,
# env.beta-readiness, and nested packages/database/.env.
.env
.env.*
env.test
env.beta
env.beta-readiness
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/env.test
**/env.beta
**/env.beta-readiness
# ...but DO keep the redacted templates tracked (no real secret ever ends in .example):
!*.example
!**/*.example

